OL,3,CMeet the Royal Welsh soldier hoping to
OL,4,Cinspire more women to join the Army
OL,6,FRepresentation of women in the UK's is
OL,7,Fstill low across the board, including
OL,8,Fin Welsh regiments, and efforts are
OL,9,Fbeing made to change that.
OL,11,FThe UK's armed forces moved to open up
OL,12,Fall roles to women in the past six
OL,13,Fyears.
OL,15,FOn a special trip to Poland, where
OL,16,FRoyal Welsh soldiers are among those
OL,17,Fon NATO's biggest military exercise in
OL,18,Fa generation, we spoke with Lance
OL,19,FCorporal Sian Beynon, who joined the
OL,20,Farmy two yeas ago.
