OL,3,CMeet the Royal Welsh soldier hoping to
OL,4,Cinspire more women to join the Army
OL,6,FShe told ITV Cymru Wales: "I always
OL,7,Fwanted to join, but specifically the
OL,8,Finfantry because when I went to be
OL,9,Frecruited they said females don't
OL,10,Freally do that.
OL,12,F"It gives you motivation to prove a
OL,13,Fpoint and prove them wrong."
OL,15,FShe's one of just three women in the
OL,16,FRoyal Welsh regiment, but she's
OL,17,Fhopeful others can be inspired to join.
