OL,3,CMeet the Royal Welsh soldier hoping to
OL,4,Cinspire more women to join the Army
OL,6,F"It's a start, it's not enough really,
OL,7,Fbut hopefully in the next few years
OL,8,Fpeople start pushing through and
OL,9,Fcoming into the roles."
OL,11,FShe is among those taking part in
OL,12,FOperation Steadfast Defender, which
OL,13,Fhas involved more than 30 countries
OL,14,Fworking together, making it the
OL,15,Forganisation's largest exercise since
OL,16,Fthe Cold War.
OL,18,FMajor Simon Davies says stereotypes
OL,19,Fabout the armed forces sometimes stop
OL,20,Fwomen from signing up.
