OL,3,CMeet the Royal Welsh soldier hoping to
OL,4,Cinspire more women to join the Army
OL,6,FHe said: "I think when people see what
OL,7,Fwe do and some of the myths gradually
OL,8,Fdissipate, we'll have more females
OL,9,Fwishing to join.
OL,11,F"I think it's seen as being a very
OL,12,Ftough job, and it can be challenging.
OL,13,FI think it's seen as being male only,
OL,14,Fand traditionally people think
OL,15,Finfantry is something not for them,
OL,16,Fbut I think that again as we have more
OL,17,Fand more female soldiers come through
OL,18,Fthey'll see examples and people they
OL,19,Fcan follow."
