OL,3,CMeet the Royal Welsh soldier hoping to
OL,4,Cinspire more women to join the Army
OL,6,FBut it's not only infantry roles that
OL,7,Fare available. Lance Corporal Meg
OL,8,FAspara is a mechanic attached to the
OL,9,Finfantry for this exercise.
OL,11,F"I just wanted something new," she
OL,12,Fsaid. "I wanted to be different. I
OL,13,Fwanted to go home and say I'm in the
OL,14,Farmy but I do this.
OL,16,F"Having a purpose and having something
OL,17,Fto put towards things, like being able
OL,18,Fto fix a gun is unreal, if you cant
OL,19,Ffix it it doesn't work and you've got
OL,20,Fnothing to protect yourself with, it's
OL,21,Fmonumental."
